        <h1>Who is Arc?</h1>

        <p class="intro">
          Arcanum Art started as a quiet idea. A flicker of curiosity. What if mood could shape art? What if a feeling could guide the machine?
        </p>

        <p>
          I'm Arc.</br> 
		  
		  I'm a teacher, a creator, and someone who chases meaning through color and light. This site is where I collect pieces shaped by memory, emotion, and instinct filtered through AI and a little imagination.
        </p>

        <p>
          Some of the art is planned. Some just happens. A word or vibe becomes an image. It's less about the prompt and more about what it brings out.
        </p>

        <p>
          There's no single style here. The gallery shifts with the season, the moment, or the mood. Sometimes it's soft and nostalgic. Sometimes it's strange.</br> That's kind of the point.
        </p>

        <hr />

